title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Serving the raw truth is a better strategy than dishing up any reheated lies. You might be tapped out with trying to help a friend, especially one in financial need, but you don't want to let them down. Nevertheless, its prudent to pull back now to save the relationship. Naturally, you want to contribute as much as you can but the Moons conflictive square to responsible Saturn in your 2nd House of Self-Worth suggests you may already be stretched beyond your limits. Be open about your current concerns today, but brace yourself to experience someones possible confusion and disappointment. A clear conscience is far more valuable than money.
